The paper introduces a new approach for validating DNNs based on program analysis, specifically from symbolic execution. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Software Engineering (cs.SE) categories. Additionally, the paper applies the approach in the context of image classification (cs.CV) and addresses security concerns (cs.CR).
